64
00:03:41.875 --> 00:03:43.125
[car horn honks]

65
00:03:49.375 --> 00:03:50.750
[Barry chuckles]

66
00:03:53.708 --> 00:03:57.000
♪ We're a hit and I think we deserve it ♪

67
00:03:57.083 --> 00:03:59.791
