68
00:03:59.875 --> 00:04:03.083
♪ Also. it means that this tour de force ♪

69
00:04:03.166 --> 00:04:05.375
♪ Will not be forced to tour ♪

70
00:04:05.458 --> 00:04:08.375
[Dee Dee] To Eleanor!
May she run for eternity!

71
00:04:08.458 --> 00:04:10.125
[all] To Eleanor!

72
00:04:11.916 --> 00:04:14.541
♪ Cheers to a show that's so inspiring ♪

73
00:04:15.208 --> 00:04:18.250
♪ It's almost too much to sit through ♪

74
00:04:18.833 --> 00:04:21.500
♪ And if we run
That might mean one more thing ♪

75
00:04:21.583 --> 00:04:23.208
♪ That in ten years or so ♪

76
00:04:23.291 --> 00:04:25.333
♪ We'll do Eleanor Two! ♪

77
00:04:25.416 --> 00:04:28.625
♪ I can predict
